{"id":277390,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【麻辣总局】一不小心说了句实话/","date":"2013-02-01T11:11:29Z","modified":"2013-04-05T02:11:24Z","title":"【麻辣总局】一不小心说了句实话","content":"<p>共青团山西省委官方微博30日发布一则微博痛斥申纪兰，称其“任何时候都代表，但是一次也没有代表过人民”并发问“你是怎样被选举的”，网友赞此番言论犀利，但也有人担心发布者“被临时”。31日，共青团山西省委官方微博连发四遍声明：系维护人员误操作所发。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%8d%e5%b0%8f%e5%bf%83%e8%af%b4%e4%ba%86%e5%8f%a5%e5%ae%9e%e8%af%9d/twgvf/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-277391\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/tWgvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"237\" /></a></p>\n<p>30日，共青团山西省委官方微博怒斥申纪兰12次当选人大代表，是对人大代表制度的公开亵渎。</p>\n<p>31日，@山西共青团发布消息称：1月30日下午，山西共青团官方微博维护人员在工作时，不慎转出了一条新浪某个人实名微博关于申纪兰代表的贴子。现郑重声明，此微博内容不代表团山西省委观点，纯系操作失误。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%8d%e5%b0%8f%e5%bf%83%e8%af%b4%e4%ba%86%e5%8f%a5%e5%ae%9e%e8%af%9d/elylz/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-277392\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-277392\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/ElylZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"424\" height=\"1048\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/ElylZ.jpg 424w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/ElylZ-121x300.jpg 121w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/ElylZ-414x1024.jpg 414w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 424px) 100vw, 424px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>@刘芮东：山西共青团的官微怒斥申纪兰当选12任人大代表，是对人大代表制度的公开亵渎。</p>\n<p>@扭发条猴子：昨山西共青团怒斥申纪兰后，今日连发四遍撇清声明，四遍！四遍啊！这真真是吓尿了？</p>\n<p>@任建宇305：一不小心说了句实话，痛苦成啥样了。（部分内容摘自喷嚏）</p>\n<div></div>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,10466,13789],"tags":[9231,21684,20837]}